{"tid":1214781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大律師公會：關注有影片顯示警用非必要武力","createTime":"2019-06-13T05:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T06:20:52.000Z","uid":20933,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8d0c078ad255139480c507c6496e8d8d87c39ea1","tid":1214781,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190613/s00001/17e25843f3a5780190ef4342e97d2268.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190613%2Fs00001%2F17e25843f3a5780190ef4342e97d2268.jpg&h=4e6abd0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反對修訂《逃犯條例》市民昨日（12日）在金鐘與警方爆發激烈衝突，大律師公會今日（13日）發表聲明，強烈譴責任何一方的暴力行為，呼籲公眾繼續以耐心及理性的態度表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n大律師公會表示，嚴重關注有影片顯示警方作出罔顧示威者及前線記者安全行為，「包括在示威者似乎沒有對警方或公眾造成威脅下，向一些手無寸鐵的示威者，甚至一些顯然是記者的在場人士使用非必要的武力」，顯示警方似乎已遠超其行使維持公共秩序的合法權力。<br />\n<br />\n大律師公會指出，政府必須深切自省是否堅持修例，任何認為本身是需要向公眾負責任的政府必然會暫緩修訂，與社會各方進行對話，重新考慮立場。"},{"pid":"bdec52f9d1aa95db25140daf9d618a50f64039ab","tid":1214781,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:18:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190613/s00001/1560401717930/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190613%2Fs00001%2F1560401717930%2F&d=lXSk0n6jiDV9AqJ6X6RhLkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=981cb4e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190613%2Fs00001%2F1560401717930%2F&h=4585d3f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190613/s00001/1560401717930/</a>"},{"pid":"cd19f02d1371cdab2b20981d706ceb8af661c841","tid":1214781,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a740cc21b7c5b76176552370b38d718c7a7a5c8","tid":1214781,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:20:13.000Z","msg":"可唔可能採取法律行動？"},{"pid":"f3ce7824618c0c3cb5fd228967150419b50477b1","tid":1214781,"uid":231785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"得個講字，落案告班黑警啦"},{"pid":"a0eafa2f7b73301fd4c40a9d44397661a98f3043","tid":1214781,"uid":132941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:20:52.000Z","msg":"大律師公會係香港嘅良心"}]}